<DIV>(gracious I wish i could find an edit button or something like that)</DIV>
<DIV>Hiya all.&nbsp; I truly hope that this is the correct place for this...&nbsp; Missions and quests seemed closer than all the other listings I have found so far though.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>For reference below, I will detail two of the groups that I tried to pull these missions with (3-boxed):</DIV>
<DIV>Group 1: 70 Cleric (DE), 69 Mage (DE, Agnostic), 61 Shaman (Barb, Tribunal)&nbsp; **all these are apprehensive to the Dark Reign Camp**</DIV>
<DIV>Group 2: 62 Warrior (WE, Rallos Zek), 61 Shaman (Barb, Tribunal), 57 Bard (WE, Agnostic)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Problems:</DIV>
<DIV>With BOTH groups, I could only get the ones standing at the fire to talk to me...&nbsp; the ones closest to the wall wouldn't talk to me (seemed like my faction wasn't high enough) and the rest would just give a message stating that my group does not meet the requirements for requesting a mission, or something to that effect.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>With Group 1, if the cleric requested the adventure from the ones in the middle, I would get a message stating that the average level of the group was too low.&nbsp; If I tried to get with the shaman, I would get a message stating that the average level was too high.&nbsp; This had me scratching my head so I thought maybe the level spread was only 7 levels (even though It was stated that the level spread would be 10 on one of the threads by a dev...&nbsp; I will post link to that thread once I am able to find it again) so I tried with Group 2.&nbsp; If my shaman requested, the group average was too high.&nbsp; If the Bard requested, the average was too low (please note a <U>5</U> level difference here).</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Questions:</DIV>
<DIV>Is anyone else able to get a mission from these camps? Is there a quest or something you have to do before you can get the missions?</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Thank you very much for any help that you can provide (even if it's just pointing me into the right direction so I can fix my own idiocy...&nbsp; whatever, I just want to be able to enjoy the expansion), and sorry for the incomplete post before... not sure exactly what happened there</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
