<DIV></DIV>
<P>you dont give tokens to merchants..</P>
<P></FONT>&nbsp;</P>
<P>you take them SE of nagafen's lair zone in (south of evil camp) at the lip of the lava pit, there are "allliance" wayfarers there, you give the token to either the male (evil) or female (good) to gain faction with the tokens, do this after each&nbsp; mission</FONT></P>
<P></FONT>&nbsp;</P>
<P>if you hail those two npcs in the camps&nbsp; [without the titles below their names] they actually tell you to give them tokens to prove your loyalty etc...</FONT></P>
				
