				<td rowspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" style="text-align: justify;" width="100%" valign=top>
				It appears that there are incrementing awards at each camp as you increase your faction.  Someone just mentioned that they won a free AA for raising their faction at one camp.<br><br>You can use the Wayfarers over east of the Nagafen entrance to turn in tokens for the faction you want and even perform solo tasks that effect your faction.<br><br>The tasks themselves and the gear from each camp seems to be the same.  You will, however, have to trade your crystals for the opposite sides crystals but I don't really see this as any more restricting than the LDON camp items.
				
